# ── Vendored reference trees (read-only, clone separately per SETUP.md) ──
# godot-master / pcsx-redux-main / splashedit-main are reference sources we
# don't modify. Users who need them clone from their upstream repos.
# psxsplash-main is tracked — we carry local patches there (see
# docs/psxsplash-improvements.md). Future: extract to patches/psxsplash/.
godot-master/
pcsx-redux-main/
splashedit-main/
lua-gdextension-main/
UnrealEngine-5.7.4-release/
blender-main/

# Release-zip build output (created by scripts/py/build-release.py).
PS1Godot.zip

# ── Godot 4.x (.NET) ──
godot-ps1/.godot/
godot-ps1/.import/
godot-ps1/export.cfg
godot-ps1/export_presets.cfg
godot-ps1/.mono/
godot-ps1/bin/
godot-ps1/obj/
godot-ps1/*.csproj.user
godot-ps1/*.sln.DotSettings.user
godot-ps1/project.godot*.tmp

# ── Splashpack build output (authored scene → PSX binary) ──
godot-ps1/build/
*.splashpack
*.vram
*.spu
*.iso
*.cue

# ── GDExtension (PS1Lua script language) build artifacts ──
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/build/
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/lib/godot-cpp/
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/.sconsign.dblite
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/**/*.o
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/**/*.obj
# Autocomplete data file is regenerated per scons build from luaapi.hh.
# Kept out of git so the tree doesn't flap with every rebuild.
godot-ps1/addons/ps1godot/scripting/src/ApiData.gen.cpp

# ── psxsplash runtime build artifacts ──
# Keep source + our patches; ignore compiled outputs.
psxsplash-main/psxsplash.elf
psxsplash-main/psxsplash.ps-exe
psxsplash-main/psxsplash.map
psxsplash-main/**/*.o
psxsplash-main/**/*.d
psxsplash-main/**/*.dep
psxsplash-main/**/*.bin
psxsplash-main/**/*.cpe
psxsplash-main/third_party/**/*.a

# ── JetBrains Rider / IntelliJ ──
.idea/workspace.xml
.idea/tasks.xml
.idea/usage.statistics.xml
.idea/shelf/
.idea/**/contentModel.xml
*.iml

# ── Visual Studio / VS Code ──
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user

# ── Claude Code workspace files ──
.claude/
.sentry-native/

# ── OS cruft ──
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# ── tools/ (Python helpers) ──
# Byte-code caches and any stray output dropped in the tools dir when a
# script was run without an explicit output argument.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
tools/*.wav
tools/*.mid
tools/*.splashpack

# ── Release staging ──
# Built by scripts/build-release.py; attached to GitHub Releases.
# Not tracked in the repo itself.
dist/

# ── Local-only config ──
.env
.env.local
*.local.json

# ── "The Monitor" jam game (out-of-tree project) ──
# The PSXSplash Game Jam 2026 entry built on top of PS1Godot. Engine +
# plugin live in the repo; the jam game's scene, Lua, assets, the
# monitor-specific docs, and the placeholder regenerator script stay
# local. The general lessons learned (PS1FixedCamera proposal, memory
# entries) DO get committed since they apply project-wide.
godot-ps1/scenes/monitor/
godot-ps1/lua/monitor/
godot-ps1/assets/monitor/
docs/the-monitor-*.md
scripts/regen-monitor-assets.py
scripts/regen-monitor-audio.py
scripts/rebuild_monitor_kenney.py
scripts/gen_goblin_*.py
scripts/gen_menu_assets.py
scripts/double_obj_faces.py
# Day 6: horror decal pipeline (gen + place + filter + Kenney install).
scripts/ai_horror_kenney_textures.py
scripts/horror_filter_kenney.py
scripts/force_horror_4bpp.py
scripts/gen_horror_assets.py
scripts/gen_alpha_assets.py
scripts/gen_blood_decal*.py
scripts/gen_remaining_alpha.py
scripts/gen_static_cobweb.py
scripts/place_horror_decals*.py
scripts/inspect_kenney_fbx.gd
scripts/install_kenney_skinned.gd
scripts/revert_kenney_skinned.gd
scripts/regen_backroom_tone.py
scripts/recenter_decals.py
# UVgami CLI binaries + per-model unwrap intermediates (large + jam-specific).
tools/uvgami/
